sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant U as User (Browser)
    participant WS as WebSocket
    participant ADK as ADK Runner<br/>+ LiveRequestQueue
    participant Live as Gemini Live API<br/>Conversation Model
    participant Agent as Director Agent<br/>"Loom"
    participant SG as SceneGenerator<br/>Interleaved Model
    participant MG as MusicGenerator<br/>Lyria RealTime
    participant GCS as Cloud Storage

    Note over U,GCS: Phase 1 — User speaks a story idea

    U->>WS: Binary PCM audio (16 kHz)
    WS->>ADK: send_realtime(audio)
    ADK->>Live: Stream PCM audio
    Note right of Live: VAD detects<br/>end of speech

    Live->>ADK: Agent voice response (24 kHz PCM)
    ADK->>WS: Audio chunks + text events
    WS->>U: Binary PCM → AudioPlayback<br/>JSON text → ConversationPanel

    Note over U,GCS: Phase 2 — Agent decides to create a scene (tool call)

    Live->>ADK: tool_call: create_scene(title, prompt, mood, ...)
    ADK->>Agent: Execute tool
    Agent->>WS: notify: {type: "generating", active: true}
    WS->>U: Show generation spinner + timer

    Note over U,GCS: Phase 3 — Interleaved scene generation (background task)

    Agent->>SG: generate_scene(prompt, style_ref)
    SG->>SG: Build prompt with characters,<br/>style, continuity notes

    rect rgba(124, 45, 18, 0.3)
        Note over SG: Gemini Interleaved API Call
        SG->>SG: response_modalities=["TEXT","IMAGE"]
        SG-->>SG: Stream: text → image → text → image ...
    end

    loop Each image part
        SG->>GCS: save_media(image_bytes)
        GCS-->>SG: public URL
    end

    SG-->>Agent: SceneResult(blocks, metadata)

    Note over U,GCS: Phase 4 — Music generation (parallel background task)

    Agent->>MG: generate(mood, tempo)
    MG->>MG: Lyria RealTime streaming
    MG->>GCS: save_media(wav_bytes)
    GCS-->>MG: public URL
    MG-->>Agent: music URL

    Note over U,GCS: Phase 5 — Frontend receives and renders

    Agent->>WS: notify: {type: "interleaved_scene", blocks, metadata}
    WS->>U: Scene data → StoryCanvas renders<br/>interleaved text+image blocks

    Agent->>WS: notify: {type: "music", url, mood}
    WS->>U: Music URL → audio player

    Agent->>WS: notify: {type: "story_state_update", bible}
    WS->>U: Story Bible panel updates

    Agent->>WS: notify: {type: "generating", active: false}
    WS->>U: Hide spinner

    Note over U,GCS: Phase 6 — Agent returns tool result, continues talking

    Agent-->>ADK: tool_result: "Scene 1 created successfully"
    ADK->>Live: Tool result
    Live->>ADK: Agent voice: "There we go! What do you think?"
    ADK->>WS: Audio + text
    WS->>U: Agent voice plays + transcript shown

    Note over U,GCS: Phase 7 — Session auto-saved to Firestore
